You think she was the in-flight entertainment.
你觉得她是飞行中的娱乐

194
00:10:03,730 --> 00:10:06,900
Anything you want to tell us about the bone bits you care about?
对于那些你所关心的骨块 有什么要告诉我们的吗？

195
00:10:07,040 --> 00:10:11,630
Supra-orbital margin is rounded,suggesting a male.
眼窝的上缘是圆的，表明是个男性

