00:13:31,440 --> 00:13:33,610
but figure out how their remains were scattered.
还要找出这些残骸是怎样分散开的

264
00:13:33,690 --> 00:13:36,210
Not by being cut up. That's for sure.
不是被切开的，那是肯定的了

265
00:13:36,340 --> 00:13:40,440
Now we've eliminated blades.
现在我们已经排除刀割了

266
00:13:42,210 --> 00:13:45,050
Never freeze on me again.
别再对我发愣了

267
00:13:45,200 --> 00:13:47,390
I find Dr. Goodman scary.
我发现Goodman博士很吓人

268
00:13:47,540 --> 00:13:51,830
Well,I'm never trusting any of us again.We're that good at lying
好了，我不会再信任我们中的任何人了 我们都那么擅长说谎

269
00:13:52,010 --> 00:13:54,820
We're going to do much better.
我们要做的更好

270
00:13:58,860 --> 00:14:00,970
Well,you know,I have to admit
你知道, 我不得不承认

271
00:14:01,100 --> 00:14:05,640
Jesse Caine's file on his father is both well-organized and complete.
Jesse Caine关于他父亲的档案 既有条理又完整

272
00:14:05,980 --> 00:14:09,410
Yep. The main suspect is his father's girlfriend.
是，主要的嫌疑犯是她父亲的女友

273
00:14:09,640 --> 00:14:12,010
--Karen Anderson. --No alibi.
- Karen Anderson - 没有不在犯罪现场的证明

274
00:14:12,160 --> 00:14:15,100
And,since they were living together at the time of the disappearance,
还有，因为在失踪时他们一起住

275
00:14:15,210 --> 00:14:18,730
she remains in the house,and has access to their joint accounts.
她就继续在那房子里 并可以使用他们的共用帐号

276
00:14:18,840 --> 00:14:20,180
How much money are we talking about?
大概涉及多少钱？

277
00:14:20,330 --> 00:14:23,590
Max Caine,he was a stockbroker.He was worth millions.
Max Caine, 他是股票经纪人 身价百万

278
00:14:23,710 --> 00:14:27,660
But,you know,after seven years missing,the courts will declare him officially dead.
可是，你知道, 失踪了7年 法庭已经官方地宣布了他的死亡

279
00:14:27,860 --> 00:14:30,780
By that time,she could have siphoned out most of the money.
那时候，她就可以取走所有的钱了

280
00:14:30,890 --> 00:14:36,260
So I say we go visit Miss Anderson,and we'll know pretty fast if she's a suspect.
所以我说要去拜访这位Anderson小姐 很快我们就会知道她是不是个嫌疑犯了

281
00:14:36,470 --> 00:14:37,640
How?
怎么办？

282
00:14:37,900 --> 00:14:40,310
How?Subtle psychological indicators.
怎么办？微妙的心理变化

283
00:14:40,500 --> 00:14:41,970
I looked those up on the Internet.
我在因特网上查过这些了

284
00:14:42,080 --> 00:14:46,420
Body language,sweat,tonal quality,shifty eyes.
身体语言，汗，声调的变化 多变的眼神

285
00:14:46,530 --> 00:14:47,210
Hey,you know what?
嘿，你知道吗？

286
00:14:47,330 --> 00:14:51,820
I don't go poking around your bone stuff,okay? Just leave the human stuff to me.
我可不会管你骨头的事，好吗？ 就让我处理观察人方面的事 

287
00:14:52,080 --> 00:14:54,810
Why has Max's disappearance become a matter for the FBI?
为什么Max的失踪变成FBI的事情了?

288
00:14:54,880 --> 00:14:57,700
Max's disappearance is not an FBI matter.
Max的失踪不是FBI的事情

289
00:14:57,900 --> 00:14:59,350
You're an FBI agent.
你是个FBI探员

290
00:14:59,480 --> 00:15:02,530
Human remains were found in the course of a federal investigation.
在联邦调查过程中有人的残骸被发现

291
00:15:02,610 --> 00:15:05,850
Agent Booth is tasked with the job of identifying them.
Booth探员的任务就是确定他们的身份

292
00:15:05,940 --> 00:15:09,890
