00:15:14,230 --> 00:15:18,120
Because I know Max's son Jesse accuses me of Max's murder.
因为我知道Max的儿子Jesse 控告我是害Max的凶手

296
00:15:18,350 --> 00:15:20,210
Why do you think he suspects you?
你为什么认为他怀疑你呢?

297
00:15:20,400 --> 00:15:22,250
Because of the age difference between me and Max.
因为我和Max之间的年龄差距

298
00:15:22,370 --> 00:15:25,720
Because I'm still living in the house.Because,after five years,
因为我仍旧住在这房子里 因为5年以后

299
00:15:25,830 --> 00:15:28,400
